
1. Create Site for company name eg 'company A'
2. Make  a not of the handle
3. Create a group with same handle as the company name handle
4. Create user - use the Username filed to add the 5 digit company number
5. Activate user on the right hand side of user edit screen
6. Add user permissions to group you have created at step 3

NB For additional language site repeat above steps but miss out step 3